<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>发呆 - 标签 - 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E5%8F%91%E5%91%86/</link><description>发呆 - 标签 - 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><copyright>This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International License.</copyright><lastBuildDate>Sun, 16 Nov 2008 00:33:58 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E5%8F%91%E5%91%86/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>认真去做一件事</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/seriously-do-something/</link><pubDate>Sun, 16 Nov 2008 00:33:58 +0000</pubDate><author><name>大大的小蜗牛</name><uri>https://eallion.com/</uri><email>eallions@gmail.com</email></author><guid>https://www.eallion.com/seriously-do-something/</guid><description>这篇文章介绍了作者对于认真对待事物的态度和观点。作者认为认真对待事物的人很美丽，可以通过认真去做很多事情。作者表示自己现在正在认真地发呆，并且坚信这是不可能的。作者还提到自己对待任何事情都是认真的，但幸好自己并不是工作狂。</description></item><item><title>无与伦比的寂寞</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/unparalleled-lonely/</link><pubDate>Sat, 15 Nov 2008 00:32:01 +0000</pubDate><author><name>大大的小蜗牛</name><uri>https://eallion.com/</uri><email>eallions@gmail.com</email></author><guid>https://www.eallion.com/unparalleled-lonely/</guid><description>文章讲述了作者对寂寞的感受和思考，认为时间比寂寞更加无法逾越。</description></item></channel></rss>